description: ElementManagerWeb: Table storing Ericsson-specific Element Manager Web attributes for different cells, including timestamps, cell identifiers, and timer values.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp of data record), Area_Name (geographic area of the cell), CellId (unique cell identifier), Id2 (duplicate of CellId), Id3 (likely a redundant identifier, always '1'), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (version of the data format), ElementManagerWeb.idleTimer (idle timer value), ElementManagerWeb.elementManagerWebId (Element Manager Web ID), ElementManagerWeb.absoluteTimer (absolute timer value).
